abstract: Indonesia police say DNA testing confirms terrorism suspect Abu Wardah was killed week earlier during gun battle with security forces on Sulawesi Island; Wardah was leader of Mujahedeen of Eastern Indonesia, Islamic State terrorist cell.
lead_paragraph: The suspect, known as Santoso, was killed earlier in the week in a gun battle with Indonesian security forces.

headline.main: Indonesian Police Say DNA Confirms Most Wanted Terror Suspect Is Dead
headline.print_headline: Indonesia Says It Killed Terror Leader
